    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The design for the 3 in 1 Flint Rod Striker Fire Starter Whistle makes it easy for you to use, guiding your thumb to the perfect spot to create the most leverage when gripping the striker. A whistle is integrated within the fire starter, allowing you to signal other individuals in cases of emergency. The key-ring allows for you to carry your keys, lanyard, carabiners and/or paracords along with the flint whistle to ensure that it will not be lost. You&#039;ll undoubtedly want the flint striker in cases of an emergency. You don&#039;t want to be caught without it when you are stranded in the middle of the woods. Sure you might have matches, but matches get wet, and once they are wet they are useless. The striker can easily be used when wet</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 3 in 1 Flint Rod Striker Fire Starter Whistle Orange Green Black</h2>\n  <p>The design for the 3 in 1 Flint Rod Striker Fire Starter Whistle makes it easy for you to use, guiding your thumb to the perfect spot to create the most leverage when gripping the striker. A whistle is integrated within the fire starter, allowing you to signal other individuals in cases of emergency. The key-ring allows for you to carry your keys, lanyard, carabiners and/or paracords along with the flint whistle to ensure that it will not be lost.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>EMERGENCY FIRE STARTER:</strong> The design makes it easy to use guiding you to place your thumb in the perfect spot to create the most leverage when gripping the striker</li>\n    <li><strong>SURVIVAL WHISTLE:</strong> A whistle is integrated with in the fire starter allowing you to signal other individuals in cases of emergency</li>\n    <li><strong>EVERY DAY CARRY:</strong> The key-ring allow for you to to carry your keys, lanyard, carabiners or paracord along with the flint whistle</li>\n    <li><strong>EMERGENCY USE:</strong> Emergency Preparedness, Backpacking, Survival, Camping, Every Day Carry, Boating, Hiking, Bug Out Bag</li>\n    <li>Can be used hundreds of times over and over. Ideal beginner use for learning wilderness skills as well as seasoned outdoorsman</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/wilderness_tools/FS385OR_firestarter_orange_stock2.jpg\" alt=\"The design for the 3 in 1 Flint Rod Striker Fire Starter Whistle makes it easy for you to use, guiding your thumb to the perfect spot to create\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> FSWORG-2</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886676065</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 4.25</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>You&#039;ll undoubtedly want the flint striker in cases of an emergency. You don&#039;t want to be caught without it when you are stranded in the middle of the woods. Sure you might have matches, but matches get wet, and once they are wet they are useless. The striker can easily be used when wet. Lighters work well, but they eventually run out of fuel and outlive their usefulness whereas the flint can be used for many years. It&#039;s a must-have in any pack.</p>\n  <p>This has many different uses Emergency Preparedness, Doomsday Prepper, Backpacking, Survival, Camping, Every Day Carry, Boating, Hiking, Bug out Bag, or Zombie Apocalypse. It also makes an excellent gift for Christmas, Valentines Day, Stocking Stuffer, Anniversary, Easter, Birthday, or Fathers Day.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The design for the 3 in 1 Flint Rod Striker Fire Starter Whistle makes it easy for you to use, guiding your thumb to the perfect spot to create the most leverage when gripping the striker. A whistle is integrated within the fire starter, allowing you to signal other individuals in cases of emergency. The key-ring allows for you to carry your keys, lanyard, carabiners and/or paracords along with the flint whistle to ensure that it will not be lost. You'll undoubtedly want the flint striker in cases of an emergency. You don't want to be caught without it when you are stranded in the middle of the woods. Sure you might have matches, but matches get wet, and once they are wet they are useless. The striker can easily be used when wet.",
